Dotfiles
--------

Steps to setup a new machine

1. Create an ssh key
2. Upload key to github
3. Clone this repo
4. Run link.sh
5. Install neovim
9. pip install neovim
6. Download vim-plug (for neovim)
7. nvim:PlugInstall
9. cd YouCompleteMe; ./install.py --clang-completer
10. cd nvim/plugged/powerline-fonts; ./install.sh
11. Switch to a powerline font
12. Create some bash shortcuts in ~/cd_shorties.sh
13. Update terminal colorscheme
